Hi, everything is ok. Your slide-text is inside div .overlay-2. 
But your css is not correct. 
!important goes inside the semicolon, like this:  position: absolute !important;
not outside. This is CSS and has nothing to do only with backstetch.
But you need no !important because you don't override inline css.
Example:
.overlay-2 {
position: absolute;
left:50%;
top:50%;
background: #FFF;
padding: 12px;
font-size: 28px;
color: #000;
}

